<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Cat Gear Index and its focus on practical cat grooming and home care guidance.">
  <article class="article-shell">
    <h1>About Cat Gear Index</h1>
    <p class="lead">Cat Gear Index publishes practical grooming, washing, cleanup, and home-care guidance for cat owners who want simple routines and clearer product choices.</p>
    <p>The site is built around usable articles, lightweight tools, and structured notes instead of generic roundup content. Our goal is to help readers handle everyday care tasks such as brushing, litter-area cleaning, odor control, and routine maintenance at home.</p>
    <p>Cat Gear Index does not provide veterinary diagnosis, treatment advice, or emergency guidance. For health, medication, injuries, or behavior concerns, contact a licensed veterinarian.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
